description: This Suffolk based village is located near to the towns of Bury St Edmunds and Stowmarket. Haughley Park and Woolpit are the nearest villages. Please scroll down for the full list of walks near and around Elmswell. The detailed maps below also show a range of footpaths, bridleways and cycle paths in the area.
